%h3.text-center
  You've asked to swap your vote with #{@user.swapped_with.name}!

%p
  .card.profile
    = render partial: "user/swaps/swap_profile", object: @user.swapped_with, as: "other_user"

%p.text-center
  %i.fa.fa-fw.fa-spin.fa-spinner
  We're just waiting for #{@user.swapped_with.name} to confirm the swap!
  If we don't hear back from them in 2 days, we'll cancel the swap and you can pick someone else.